external_knowledge:
Goal-scoring players refers to those who have scored at least one goal (goals_scored > 0);
 Goal-scoring prowess refers to the number of goals scored by each player (p.goals_scored);
 Ranking from highest to lowest means arranging the players in order of the most goals scored to the least.

sql:
SELECT event_id, player_id, points_awarded, minute 
FROM bonus_points 
WHERE minute > 80;
